	"version": "1.0",
	"notes": "Challenge level. Uses all obstacle types: holes (4 corners), rocks (4 cells), 8 dirt patches, 6 flowers at full HP. Multi-goal: reach 3000 points, clear all dirt, clear all flowers, collect 10 pumpkins. Score overrides increase base match values to compensate for reduced active cells. Introduces pumpkin (6th crop)."
